	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">tepples wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Was the name 「魂斗羅」 chosen for any special meaning, or just because it on-reads as 「コントラ」?</div>
<br />
<br />From the game's intro:
<br />
<br /><span style="font-size: 150%; line-height: normal">”魂斗羅”</span>とは、
<br />熱い闘魂とゲリラ戦術の
<br />素質を持つ、最強の闘士の
<br />呼称である。
<br />
<br />I suppose the "[hot] fighting spirit" (熱い闘魂) could be part of it, though it's most likely that those characters were chosen solely for their readings.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
